update quest_template set requestitemstext = 'Without you, we would still be in the dark. Who knows, maybe you stopped another war between the Horde and the Alliance? You are a hero of Theramore, for all of the work you have done to ease the tensions, and solve this mystery.\n\nFor this, I would like you to take one of these weapons from my personal armory.\n\nConcerning the Vengeful Mariner. Sailors coming to Theramore have reported seeing a shadowy figure stalking the coast. A question does remain, why was this figure so important to the deserters?\n\nI would not lose sleep, this is not a mystery for us to worry about, or another investigation to be launched, let them keep their mariner in whatever grave he occupies.' where entry = 40565;
